description: This file defines an enumeration 'Rashi' representing Indian astrology zodiac signs, along with associated properties and methods for display labels, starting letters, and string parsing.

classes.name: Rashi
classes.description: An enum capturing Indian astrology zodiac signs with methods for display and parsing.

methods.name: label
methods.description: Returns the display label for each Rashi.

methods.name: startingLetters
methods.description: Provides auspicious starting letters for names associated with each Rashi.

methods.name: fromString
methods.description: Converts a string to the corresponding Rashi enum value, defaulting to 'mesha' if no match.
